      "date": "2012-11-01 02:15:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/0f26aeca-23c7-11e2-bb20-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
