      },
      "date": "2012-11-02 14:51:46.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAndreas, you are exactly right about the mdd device and the helper.  Think mdd2obd_dev(mdd)->obd_name gives me what I need.  Took a fair amount of looking around before I discovered that.  Thanks for the hint.\n\nAbout the early unlock of mdd_tobj, I thought the existing unlock at that point was needed due to locking done in later code.  Didn't realize until more careful review that later locks were all being done on other objs.  Will fix this in the next patch rev leaving the only unlock after cleanup:, as your earlier comments clearly indicated was your intent.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
